Tailwind CSS use with vite
npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer(this is dependency)
npx tailwindcss init -p (It generate the tailwind file)
now open tailwind file and pest inside the content
 content: [
    "./index.html",
    "./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
  ],

  now open index.css and pest inside it at the top
  @tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
npm run dev (for start the project on localhost)